{"tid":319572,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"本地叫雞市場上係咪得返老雞?","createTime":"2017-07-13T02:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T18:50:12.000Z","uid":83913,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a3e874744368316c65c6d36a24517cdbdb4af17a","tid":319572,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:10:35.000Z","msg":"講緊傳統果隻一樓一<br />\n<br />\n除咗老咗色衰粉褪既女人，仲有邊d人會去做雞?<br />\n<br />\n因為後生既女仔，根本唔會去做一樓一，<br />\n<br />\n因為太過無彈性，而且搵客太被動，<br />\n<br />\n加上只能同時間服待一個客。相反，<br />\nPTGF同時間可以用電話同幾個客chat,亦係工作既一部分。收入自然更多。<br />\n<br />\n而且，PTGF等職業比起一樓一更加崇高，<br />\n唔只滿足肉體更滿足人既心靈。<br />\n<br />\n將來要結婚嫁人仲可以同個傻仔講。我賣感情，無賣身。唔似一樓一，開始咗就係一歸路。<br />\n<br />\n所以傳統一樓一應該會青黃不接，將會劃上句號?"},{"pid":"0d3b623fcc198ef55ae0a499b5cc3f26d14250bd","tid":319572,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:11:10.000Z","msg":"利申，未叫過一樓一"},{"pid":"9b89ce6eb91117d08865bd62642073381458da89","tid":319572,"uid":23707,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:11:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利申，未叫過一樓一</blockquote><br />\n咁你點知一樓一得返老雞"},{"pid":"7a5a5367472248a84c6f004eab129bf352f07c22","tid":319572,"uid":24344,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:12:49.000Z","msg":"樓主你親自上轉一樓一先開post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e50b008a8d1fc80ce37cb93417ae9c17c385846","tid":319572,"uid":48277,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:13:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>利申，未叫過一樓一</blockquote><br />\n咁你點知一樓一得返老雞</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪踢爆人"},{"pid":"7557b0d3771a64e1eb7ae1995900bea329463464","tid":319572,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:13:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>利申，未叫過一樓一</blockquote><br />\n咁你點知一樓一得返老雞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思我表達得唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgm